Additionally, this year has continued to be particularly stressful, causing some open source projects to announce that they‚Äôre taking it slow for the final month of the year. We found [the example set by the Electron project in their blog post](https://www.electronjs.org/blog/a-quiet-place-21) to be particularly poignant. Following their example, we‚Äôve decided that we also will be taking some extra time and may be slow to respond for the rest of the year.
